<div class="service-details section-spacing">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xl-9 col-lg-8 col-12">
                <div class="service-content">
                    <img src="~/images/drinking-water-tests/drinking-water-tests.jpg" alt="service-image" class="cover-img" />
                    <h3 class="main-title">Drinking Water Testing & Analysis</h3>
                    <p>
                        Our Engineers conduct routine drinking water testing to ensure potable water is safe for human consumption and make certain that water quality meets and fulfills our clients' legal requirements.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        NEWTEST ensures that water pipeline systems are monitored and tested according to Palestinian Specifications (PS) and country legislation. We provide routine drinking water testing for a variety of contaminants and provide fast and accurate reports for environmental consultants, municipalities and private businesses.
                    </p>

                    <div class="tests">
                        <p>Our laboratory conducts water testing for: </p>
                        <ul class="columns" data-column="2">
                            <li>Chloride Percentage in water pipelines after disinfection operations</li>
                            <li>Water PH level  </li>
                            <li>M- Endo agar testing water for coliforms </li>
                            <li>M fecal agar for the detection and enumeration of fecal coliforms</li>
                            <li>The proportion of salts in the water (TDS)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- /.service-content -->
            </div>
            <!-- /.col- -->

            <div class="col-xl-3 col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-8 col-12 theme-sidebar-one">
